Start Apache and radosgw.
.sp
Debian/Ubuntu:
.INDENT 3.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 start
sudo /etc/init.d/radosgw start
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
